values: Yah so school starts in a week and thats a pretty big drag. But the last few days have been perfect.

Well summer is pretty much done. And it wasnt all that great. I mean it had it's ups but most of it was just meaningless. I started getting into art again and I'm actually really excited about it. But otherwise its just been empty. I noticed its not the same doing things with a girl if I don't have actual feelings for them. I just wish that I could have something with someone like I had earlier this year. I mean granted that I don't really have feelings for that person anymore I liked the relationship and I just wish I could have something like it again. But it is a Wednesday night so I think I am gonna go do something else instead of complaining on lj.
Chad Muska (pro skater) was just on Entourage (HBO series) that made my day

Last night was really random but in a good way.
I saw someone that I hadn't seen or talked to in a long time.
And I think we are friends now? I ain't sure on that one yet.
But then I hung out with Mark which was cool and that was pretty much whats been going on.
Today I made lots of money

List 5 reasons why you are a dork. And make them good reasons. Justify them. Explain them. Be proud of it. Then pick 5 friends/dorks you know and have them do the same.

1) I still sleep in my sheets and blankets from when I was a little kid. The only thing about this that makes me a dork is that they are mickey mouse sheets and blankets but the are SO soft and awesome. And I also sleep with my stuffed bunny from when I was a child.

2) I taught myself the whole Napoleon Dynamite dance. It seemed like a good idea at the time until the move got really popular which made it really lame. But if you ask me to do it and I like you enough Ill do it for you.

3) I have all of the original Power Ranger episodes on tape and I watch them occasionally. And by occasionally I mean all the time. I like when the monsters get all big and there is a big Godzilla type fight.

4) I had cornrows and I am going to grow another large jew fro except I am catholic so it would be more like a christ fro except I do not believe in catholasism so I guess I am just a white boy with curly hair. But the point is I want to be black. 

5) The last reason I am a dork is because at the moment these songs are on my playlist on itunes 
Eamon - Fuck It(don't want you back)
Hanson - Where's The Love
Sisqo - The Thong Song
  and the two normal songs
Stephen Malkmus and The Jicks - Time For The Gravity Bong
The '89 Cubs - Oh, The Things We Put In Our Heads

Now I have to ask Gary, Sam, Koon, Juliana, and Cheryl to do the same as me and say why you are a dork

Today was so great

I woke up around 10:30 and played some super mario world on my Super Nintendo

Then I ate some leftover mac n cheese and watched entourage (Best show ever, quite possibly better than the OC)

Then I went skating with Gary and I met this guy Nick who was pretty awesome he showed us some great spots to skate in rockville. I really want to go back to this one brick bank, it was SO nice

And I am making this poster for some show that Gary is going to, I can't wait I love drawing things for other people
Who wants to see The Decemberists with me?....................Anyone?
I am back from North Carolina, and I am going skateboarding.
